 học Công Nghệ Đông Á</a></strong>. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lịch trình dự kiến</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>18:00 – 18:15: Networking</li>\n\n\n\n<li>18:15 – 18:45: Điểm tin WordPress</li>\n\n\n\n<li>18:45 &#8211; 19:15: Sử dụng WordPress cơ bản</li>\n\n\n\n<li>19:15 &#8211; 19:45: Thảo luận mở về WordPress</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Đăng ký tham gia</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Để việc chuẩn bị được tốt nhất, các bạn <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/hanoi-wordpress-meetup/events/300180394/\">đăng ký tham dự tại trang chính thức Meetup</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2024/04/08/ha-noi-wordpress-meetup-thang-04-2024/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"1146\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"Hà Nội WordPress Meetup tháng 01.2024\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2024/01/04/ha-noi-wordpress-meetup-