 Image Upload Limit</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=3078527\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-11.png?rev=3078527\" alt=\"Convert Images into WebP\"></a><p>Convert Images into WebP</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:18031:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">With new update, this plugin now take almost 50Mb ??</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tramdungxanh/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5925aa60090fdbee0fcf9afb6bc6611d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5925aa60090fdbee0fcf9afb6bc6611d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tramdungxanh/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tramdungxanh</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Năm 24, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With new update, this plugin now take almost 47,6Mb. I install this plugin for saving size, not increase size</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">DO NOT UPGRADE</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aptharsia/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b62cf05099664453a8319232fc4ae854?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b62cf05099664453a8319232fc4ae854?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aptharsia/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aptharsia</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Năm 22, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Upgraded to their pro version after using this plugin for a while. The Pro version does not work. Asked for a refund since it was an error on their part. They said there would be a fix. A month later, still didn\'t work. Asked for a refund. Never received an answer. This is not a company/developer that stands by their own policies. I will no longer use their plugin and recommend the same to all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Useful but the update has massively over-engineered the plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alrnetwork/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b905f0bfa5149aa07a29c21d327f1446?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b905f0bfa5149aa07a29c21d327f1446?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/alrnetwork/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">alrnetwork</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Năm 20, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This was a simple plugin, which basically allowed you to disable the generation of images based on their presets. However, I don\'t know when this happened.. but clearly an update came through and totally re-designed the interface, bundled a bunch of features (mostly \"Pro\" clickbait) and that would have all been fine.. if it didn\'t disable the functionality that it was already performing.<br /><br />Now, despite re-enabling the \"module\" for this plugin, to continue it\'s function of stopping the generation of various image sizes... it seems that every time there\'s an update, it wants to completely set the configuration to default.. meaning that images are being generated at the incorrect sizes once again... and you should refresh the configuration page even after saving, because sometimes it reverts back or shows the incorrect configuration.<br /><br />There was no need to bloat this plugin and basically ruin what was working perfectly fine.. But despite other complains in the support section from other users.. issues continue.<br /><br />Thanks, but I guess I\'ll be looking for a replacement.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It does its thing but PLEASE STOP WITH THE AD NOTIFICATIONS</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tokyomagic/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27b87b2f2027ec5e271294a3d03857c3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27b87b2f2027ec5e271294a3d03857c3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tokyomagic/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tokyomagic</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Năm 17, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Firstly, the plugin does its thing, it works, that is all good.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But this is yet another wordpress plugin developer who, for some reason, enjoys cluttering the admin area with advertising. I dont want my admin section, which is meant to be for managing my sites, cluttered with adverts. Why wordpress still allows this abhorrent UI practice is beyond me. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you dont want to have close their advert everytime you log in find an alternative.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fantastic plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/celebritynewspk/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b79a5ba0230c2b64fa49eb946cca973?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b79a5ba0230c2b64fa49eb946cca973?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/celebritynewspk/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pastanasta <small>(celebritynewspk)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Năm 16, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Glad to find this plugin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So good and so good support.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Could not give 5 Stars</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shirtguy72/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d64efbbbf3d1c2c733eecfc878626c3a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d64efbbbf3d1c2c733eecfc878626c3a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/shirtguy72/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">shirtguy72</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Tư 5, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Wanted so bad to leave a 5-Star but could not. At the time of this Review, the Support Thread lists multiple instances of what I ran into: ThumbPress was Great in helping pin down what thumbs I needed to keep and which to not have regenerated, \"Regenerated\" is where the 3-Star comes in. Regenerate Thumbs failed completely, had to keep this plugin installed while \"Force Regenerate Thumbnails\" plugin was used to delete the unwanted and regenerate only what I needed.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Updates break plugin - Disappointed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daphnetalbot/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3f0e8a471c26bd19a2822aee6381df2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a3f0e8a471c26bd19a2822aee6381df2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/daphnetalbot/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">daphnetalbot</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Hai 26, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This has been a love-hate sort of thing. Initially, I had some issues. I reported an issue, and it was addressed right away. At that point, I loved the plugin. It removed bloat and brought total disk storage down. So I changed my one-star review to 5.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">With the last update, image thumbnail regeneration hangs. Posting on the support forum returned no answer. A week later, someone else reported the same issue. They have also not received a response.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It is very disappointing. There is so much potential here.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">need feature</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vtrn/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/70737a469fee253af8e8727479c959c6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/70737a469fee253af8e8727479c959c6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/vtrn/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">vtrn</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Hai 12, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">The plugin is great, some images don\'t need to be saved in different sizes at all! And if this plugin doesn\'t exist, you have to refer to the codes every time and disable and re-enable them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">However there is still a long way to go… there is a major need in this plugin.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">That should add this setting to the WordPress media upload section.(when we want to create a product or post)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">So that we can choose there, with a toggle button, whether to generate sizes or not</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Ignore the Karens</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trst4215/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1c33e52c11d4998f01a323d81e3b2f6d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1c33e52c11d4998f01a323d81e3b2f6d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/trst4215/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">trst4215</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 27, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This is a fantastic plugin that performs as described. No fuss. No clutter. Super easy to use. All the naysayers below are either hopelessly incompetent or the reviews are fake. Even if there were glitches in the early versions, clearly they have since been rectified. Love it. Thank you.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great -combine with broken link checker</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomhart/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6cb56d400247b9f408ff106aad0b01f8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6cb56d400247b9f408ff106aad0b01f8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tomhart/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tomhart</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 2, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">My host is a pain about website size disk usage and this quickly knocked a whole bunch of space off. Combine with imsanity or similar to reduce the size of initial uploads and broken link checker in case you accidentally delete an image size you are using and very quickly you\'ve got a much cleaner website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:145:\"Disable Thumbnails, Regenerate Thumbnails, Compress Images, Convert to WebP, Find Unused and Large Images, Edit Images, and more with ThumbPress.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/image-sizes.5.3.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:11:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=3078527\";s:7:\"caption\";s:15:\"Module Settings\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=3078527\";s:7:\"caption\";s:18:\"Disable Thumbnails\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=3078527\";s:7:\"caption\";s:21:\"Regenerate Thumbnails\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/image-sizes/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=3078527\";s:7:\"caption\";s:20:\"Detect Unused Images\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";