(494, '_transient_cx-plugin-info-wc-affiliate', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":35:{s:4:\"name\";s:65:\"WC Affiliate – A Full-fledged Affiliate Manager for WooCommerce\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"wc-affiliate\";s:7:\"version\";s:7:\"2.2.3.3\";s:6:\"author\";s:69:\"<a href=\"https://codexpert.io/?utm_campaign=author-uri\">Codexpert</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/codexpert/\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:2:{s:9:\"codexpert\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/codexpert/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f599c530dba24bee22ae41a223176ad8?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:14:\"Codexpert, Inc\";}s:7:\"mukto90\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mukto90/\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7b748f98294e3d13301ec63e38d85f95?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:12:\"Nazmul Ahsan\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"6.3.4\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"7.4\";s:16:\"requires_plugins\";a:0:{}s:6:\"rating\";i:96;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:10;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:11;s:11:\"support_url\";s:50:\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wc-affiliate/\";s:15:\"support_threads\";i:0;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:200;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:4592;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2023-09-13 5:52am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2021-06-22\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:58:\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/?utm_campaign=plugin-uri\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:9807:\"<p>Planning to launch an affiliate program for your WooCommerce store? 🤔</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ve come to the right place and are probably looking at the best solution available for affiliate marketing of your WooCommerce store.</p>\n<p>Launching an affiliate program alongside your traditional marketing efforts is likely to give you extraordinary sales growth if done properly. Using WC Affiliate you can launch a WordPress affiliate program on your WooCommerce-based store within minutes without hiring a developer! 🎉</p>\n<h3>🤗 <strong>WHY WC AFFILIATE?</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;s exclusively built for running WP affiliate programs on WooCommerce stores.</li>\n<li>It enables a full-featured WooCommerce affiliate program</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/demo/?utm_campaign=wporg\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Live Demo</a> to figure out how affiliate management can be done before installation</li>\n<li>Powerful, accurate, and bug-free WooCommerce affiliate management solution</li>\n<li>User-friendly and easy to use</li>\n<li>Excellent graphical presentation of the statistics of WP affiliate programs</li>\n<li>Comprehensive documentation</li>\n<li>Friendly and dedicated <a href=\"https://help.codexpert.io/?utm_campaign=wporg\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">customer support team</a></li>\n<li>Fully customizable dashboard</li>\n<li>Automated payout system that integrates with Paypal and Stripe</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Have any confusion? Feel free to <a href=\"https://help.codexpert.io/tickets/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">contact our support.</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/?utm_campaign=wporg\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WC Affiliate</a> is a cleanly coded powerful plugin aimed at facilitating a WP affiliate program for your WooCommerce store. It has all the necessary features such as affiliate performance tracking, short link generation, email message customization, cross-domain cookie sharing, banner building, multi-level commission setting, excellent graphical presentation, automatic payout to affiliates, etc. Described below are the features and functionalities of this WooCommerce affiliate management solution-</p>\n<h3>🎯 REFERRAL TRACKING</h3>\n<p>WC Affiliate accurately tracks affiliate referrals on your WooCommerce store. You can set any length of cookie validity using this affiliate management plugin. Higher cookie length is likely to inspire people to sign up as your affiliate. This WooCommerce affiliate plugin also lets you choose if a referred visit should overwrite the previous one.</p>\n<h3>🎯 UNLIMITED NUMBER OF AFFILIATES</h3>\n<p>You can onboard as many affiliates as you want using this WooCommerce affiliate plugin. This army of affiliates might bring unimaginable sales volume to your WordPress affiliate program.</p>\n<h3>🎯 EXCELLENT REPORTING</h3>\n<p>Real-time reporting of referred visits will inform you what&#8217;s actually happening and which affiliate is doing what on your WordPress affiliate program. The report includes detailed information on visits, referrals, affiliates, transactions, and much more. You can also export the data of your WooCommerce affiliate program in CSV files as well.</p>\n<p>What makes WC Affiliate unique is its feature of reporting the data of your WooCommerce affiliate program in wonderful graphs, charts, and tables. From the summary view, both the Admin and the affiliate can view visits, referrals, conversion, earnings, and top-performing affiliate and web links in a colorful histogram, pie charts, linear graphs, and tables.</p>\n<h3>🎯 FIXED OR PERCENTAGE COMMISSION</h3>\n<p>You can set any of the two commission types for the affiliates – fixed or percentage. Product-wise or affiliate wise different commissions can be set.</p>\n<h3>🎯 PERSONALIZED EMAIL MESSAGES</h3>\n<p>Customizing the email messages makes affiliate management more personalized. You can edit the message to be given and address your affiliates by name while communicating with them.</p>\n<h3>🎯 PAYMENT METHOD INTEGRATION – (PRO)</h3>\n<p>Integrating payment methods to the WooCommece affiliate program can remove the hassle of offline payments. WC Affiliate can be seamlessly integrated with Paypal and Stripe. Affiliates can request a payout and you can easily disburse them via these payment methods.</p>\n<h3>🎯 TRANSLATION READY</h3>\n<p>Translating your WooCommerce affiliate program is important as you might get affiliates from various countries and languages when the affiliate marketing is operated internationally. WC Affiliate is translation ready, meaning it will seamlessly correspond to any translation plugin. You can use popular translation plugins like <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/loco-translate/https://wordpress.org/plugins/loco-translate/\" rel=\"ugc\">Loco Translate</a> for translating your WooCommerce affiliate program.</p>\n<h3>🎯 CSV EXPORT</h3>\n<p>Most of the time you need to save your WooCommerce affiliate program data to share with a superior, marketing team, or for other purposes. You can easily store the valuable data of your WooCommerce affiliate program using the CSV Export feature of WC Affiliate and never worry about data loss anymore.</p>\n<h3>🎯 BANNER BUILDER – (PRO)</h3>\n<p>As a business owner, you need to run sales promotions or discount offers often on your WooCommerce affiliate program. For that, you can easily create web banners and invite your affiliates to use those. Affiliates can use those banners on any website – be that a WordPress site or not.</p>\n<h3>🎯 SHORTLINK GENERATOR – (PRO)</h3>\n<p>WC Affiliate makes affiliate management easier by giving you control to allow affiliates to generate short links so that they can share a smart likable link with their audience. Affiliates in that case can generate an unlimited number of short links and can use custom strings during affiliate marketing. Here is an example:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Long link: <a href=\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/?ref=123</a></li>\n<li>Shortlink: <a href=\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">https://codexpert.io/go/wca</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎯 CROSS-DOMAIN COOKIE SHARING – (PRO)</h3>\n<p>WC Affiliate enables the affiliates to share the affiliate URL of one site and track it on another allowing them to use one nice URL instead of many long URLs.</p>\n<p>It helps the admins with better affiliate management by connecting multiple sites and to bring all into the affiliate system so that the affiliates become manageable from a single site.</p>\n<h3>🎯 MULTILEVEL COMMISSION – (PRO)</h3>\n<p>Gain exponential business growth from the army of affiliates you have with WC Affiliate multilevel commission! The most popular Multilevel Marketing concept is applied in this WooComemrce affiliate plugin. Affiliates will have their affiliates and then 2nd level affiliates will have theirs. This can go on upto the level the business owner/admin predetermines.</p>\n<p>Admin can set as many levels as he wants with different commission amounts/percentages at each level. Setting up these levels will ensure perfect commission distribution and bring exponential growth to your affiliate marketing program.</p>\n<p>👉 Try the<a href=\"https://codexpert.io/wc-affiliate/demo/?utm_campaign=wporg\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Live Demo</a> to experience the full potential of WC Affiliate.<br />\n👉 Connect with our<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/codexpert.io\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">official Facebook page</a> and get the latest updates and deals announcements.<br />\n👉 Go through the <a href=\"https://help.codexpert.io/docs/wc-affiliate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">documentation</a> for better usability of the WC Affiliate.<br />\n👉 Interact with other CoDesigner users on our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2074618249320463\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">official Facebook group</a>.</p>\n<p>💰 Grow with us by joining our <a href=\"https://codexpert.io/affiliates/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">affiliate program</a> and earn up to 25% commission on your sales. 💸</p>\n<p><strong>Grow your business using our other</strong> <a href=\"https://codexpert.io/products/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>fantastic plugins</strong></a> 🔔🔔</p>\n<p>🔥 <a href=\"https://pluggable.io/coschool/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">CoSchool</a> &#8211; Create a professional eLearning platform on any WordPress website with all the necessary tools t