://profiles.wordpress.org/cutero/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cutero</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Bảy 7, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you so much, it works perfectly.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great! works fine for now</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ehwh/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/609e63312e025c8f5c0cb9378488213d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/609e63312e025c8f5c0cb9378488213d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ehwh/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ehwh</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Hai 24, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very good plugin, just what i needed to show a navigation menu to logged in users. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:97:\"Restrict Elementor Widgets based on different conditions. Works for any widgets from any plugins.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/restrict-elementor-widgets.1.4.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:79:\"https://ps.w.org/res