 vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 22, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Best, fast support. Immediately solved issue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Plugin Great Support !!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jporret/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/37b733b545aea005be1b9fdfccb1cc33?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/37b733b545aea005be1b9fdfccb1cc33?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jporret/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jporret</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Một 2, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Great <strong>Plugin </strong>Great <strong>Support </strong>!!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Easy to use and very complete plugin.<br />Responsive and competent support!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Support and Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/comikwebsites/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6366c31465138ca1f27867fa205dae2a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6366c31465138ca1f27867fa205dae2a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/comikwebsites/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Comik Websites <small>(comikwebsites)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Hai 4, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I needed a plugin to give my checkout experience some sprucing up for the user experience. The variety of options for the paid version adds a lot of flexibility and nice styling options. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I also had a manor issue with plugin connectivity on my end, and in my frantic attempts for assistance, the support staff was very helpful. I appreciate the assistance to keep my website building on track.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect support and good plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/keggy/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/17d2b6851a0a4f372303df189f56516a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/17d2b6851a0a4f372303df189f56516a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/keggy/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">keggy</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Một 30, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Very very good plugin and perfect support! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Tested and bought the Pro version</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/walshie1987/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55ca32f461d2452c6ac402646035845f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/55ca32f461d2452c6ac402646035845f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/walshie1987/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">walshie1987</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười Một 2, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Removing my original 5* rating of this plugin. I was basically offered a 3 month extention on the paid version of this plugin if I left a 5 start review for the free version. Wrongly, I did that.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I bought the Pro version and it just never worked, the response from support about the standard feature not working was \"It was not designed to work that way\" - That was about the email templates not working, the only part I bought the Pro version for.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I was waiting a month for a fix to an issue, so I was patient. They kept telling me that they were looking into the issue, but I had a login tracker on my site, they had never even logged in, once I notified them of this, they logged in the next day and said it couldn\'t be fixed. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I requested a refund and weeks later it\'s still \"Processing\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">So although my review isn\'t specifically about the plugin itself, it\'s about the ethics of the company and the poor support offered.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Should have never trusted a developer who bribes you with an extention to the subscription in return for a 5* review.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Found this plugin really helpful when customising various pages in my store. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It\'s very simple if you have have no coding knowledge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">I decided to buy the Pro version so I could edit email templates too, this feature alone was worth the cost! It will be a key plugin to my store!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast support and great plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tilbed/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7d2890cd4cac36f8a0f0c523b0654794?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7d2890cd4cac36f8a0f0c523b0654794?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tilbed/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tilbed</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Mười 26, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Responded quick when I had a question and add good functionality to your site. Really love the email designer :)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Followup - to my previous review.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzintars/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c9f0ce4fb2aa0a8ae759a0df31fc0ce1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c9f0ce4fb2aa0a8ae759a0df31fc0ce1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzintars/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dzintars <small>(dzintars)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Chín 30, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;\n&lt;p class=\"\"&gt;I want to update my previous review and warn you about CoDesigner.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;\n&lt;p class=\"\"&gt;It used to be a good plugin, but now it is a nightmare. I have been having issues with the plugin\'s connection and activation for two months. It keeps losing connection to CoDesigner servers and asking me to activate my license. But when I try to do that, it says \"Sorry you are not allowed to access this page\".&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;\n&lt;p class=\"\"&gt;I have contacted their support many times and gave them access to my site. But they never bothered to check what\'s wrong.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;\n&lt;p class=\"\"&gt;Now my Woocommerce shop shows some random images instead of my products.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;\n\n&lt;!-- wp:paragraph --&gt;\n&lt;p class=\"\"&gt;CoDesigner is a waste of money and time. Avoid it at all costs!&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- /wp:paragraph --&gt;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Quick to help with any issues</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/howlinwolf/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6b1a734c978ccbe9f77231d5c448ef42?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6b1a734c978ccbe9f77231d5c448ef42?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/howlinwolf/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Howlinwolf</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng Chín 20, 2023</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Issue resolved within minutes of providing access to wordpress site directly, 